# Prisma model names

Do **not** use model names that start with an underscore in Prisma schemas. Prisma schema validation rejects them (P1012: "This line is invalid. It does not start with any known Prisma schema keyword").

**Bad:**
```prisma
model _Placeholder {
  id String @id @default(cuid())
}
```

**Good:**
```prisma
model Placeholder {
  id String @id @default(cuid())
}
```

Use PascalCase for model names (e.g. `User`, `RecurringExpense`, `StagedTransaction`). Use a normal name like `Placeholder` for temporary/scratch models instead of `_Placeholder`.
